is the real thing.

299
00:14:30,760 --> 00:14:32,080
Jin Guang Tower?

300
00:14:32,120 --> 00:14:33,320
The real thing?

301
00:14:33,440 --> 00:14:34,440
It's not jade.

302
00:14:34,440 --> 00:14:35,120
I see.

303
00:14:35,400 --> 00:14:36,480
He was testing you.

304
00:14:37,200 --> 00:14:38,360
Our man went there

305
00:14:38,680 --> 00:14:39,800
and found it was a trap.

306
00:14:40,360 --> 00:14:42,000
His men were waiting in Jin Guang Tower.

307
00:14:44,560 --> 00:14:45,680
The timing is too deliberate.

308
00:14:46,000 --> 00:14:47,480
He is so sensitive and suspicious.

309
00:14:47,640 --> 00:14:49,160
how could he say so much

310
00:14:49,160 --> 00:14:50,080
in front of me, a stranger?

311
00:14:52,800 --> 00:14:53,800
So now,

312
00:14:54,960 --> 00:14:56,120
he should trust you, right?

313
00:14:58,160 --> 00:14:59,120
People like him

314
00:14:59,120 --> 00:15:00,520
won't easily trust others.

315
00:15:00,520 --> 00:15:01,560
His hidden base

316
00:15:01,560 --> 00:15:03,680
would never be somewhere he doesn't control.

317
00:15:04,200 --> 00:15:04,800
So,

318
00:15:06,000 --> 00:15:07,760
the most likely place to find clues

319
00:15:07,760 --> 00:15:08,600
is still his home.

320
00:15:10,040 --> 00:15:11,680
I must gain Pang's trust

321
00:15:11,800 --> 00:15:13,400
to freely access his residence.

322
00:15:13,960 --> 00:15:14,760
But now,

323
00:15:15,120 --> 00:15:16,040
it's not enough.

324
00:15:17,000 --> 00:15:17,600
Yan,

325
00:15:18,960 --> 00:15:20,200
is there another way?

326
00:15:20,360 --> 00:15:20,960
I'm afraid of him.

327
00:15:20,960 --> 00:15:22,880
This is the most direct and effective way.

328
00:15:24,240 --> 00:15:25,360
He killed our master.

329
00:15:25,800 --> 00:15:27,040
He's our enemy.

330
00:15:27,520 --> 00:15:29,200
We must find out

331
00:15:29,200 --> 00:15:31,120
what's behind the real goods.

332
00:15:36,120 --> 00:15:36,560
Here.

333
00:15:37,720 --> 00:15:38,680
There are GPS devices

334
00:15:38,680 --> 00:15:39,720
in these earrings.

335
00:15:39,960 --> 00:15:40,640
If you encounter danger,

336
00:15:40,800 --> 00:15:41,720
send a distress signal directly.

337
00:15:42,320 --> 00:15:43,440
We will send someone to support you.

338
00:15:43,560 --> 00:15:44,360
Don't try to handle it alone.

339
00:15:46,200 --> 00:15:46,840
Don't worry.

340
00:15:47,960 --> 00:15:49,040
I will protect you.

341
00:15:49,920 --> 00:15:50,320
Here.
